{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3482 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3482 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3482","pos":[618,638]},{"content":"'this' can only be used as a lambda capture within a non-static member function","pos":[639,718]},{"pos":[725,848],"content":"You cannot pass <ph id=\"ph1\">`this`</ph> to the capture list of a lambda expression that is declared in a static method or a global function.","source":"You cannot pass `this` to the capture list of a lambda expression that is declared in a static method or a global function."},{"content":"To correct this error","pos":[858,879]},{"content":"Convert the enclosing function to a non-static method, or","pos":[889,946]},{"pos":[956,1029],"content":"Remove the <ph id=\"ph1\">`this`</ph> pointer from the capture list of the lambda expression.","source":"Remove the `this` pointer from the capture list of the lambda expression."},{"content":"Example","pos":[1038,1045]},{"content":"The following example generates C3482:","pos":[1049,1087]},{"content":"See Also","pos":[1256,1264]},{"content":"Lambda Expressions","pos":[1269,1287]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3482 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3482\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3482\"\nms.assetid: bf99558e-bef4-421c-bb16-dcd9c54c1011\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3482\n'this' can only be used as a lambda capture within a non-static member function  \n  \n You cannot pass `this` to the capture list of a lambda expression that is declared in a static method or a global function.  \n  \n### To correct this error  \n  \n-   Convert the enclosing function to a non-static method, or  \n  \n-   Remove the `this` pointer from the capture list of the lambda expression.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following example generates C3482:  \n  \n```  \n// C3482.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \n  \nclass C  \n{  \npublic:  \n   static void staticMethod()  \n   {  \n      [this] {}(); // C3482  \n   }  \n};  \n```  \n  \n## See Also  \n [Lambda Expressions](../../cpp/lambda-expressions-in-cpp.md)"}